ame/post-name</strong></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"\">It is strange that these unwanted URLs apparently redirect to the correct URLs. So:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>This URL: <a href=\"http://www.our-site.org/ca/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">http://www.our-site.org/ca/</a><strong>post-name/post-name</strong></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Redirects to: <a href=\"http://www.our-site.org/ca/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">http://www.our-site.org/ca/</a><strong>post-type-name/post-name</strong></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"\">Just regenerated the permalinks again, to be sure. And the issue is still there.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"\">Thanks again and in advance!</p>\n\n\n<ul id=\"bbp-topic-revision-log-17508752\" class=\"bbp-topic-revision-log\">\n\n	<li id=\"bbp-topic-revision-log-17508752-item-17508754\" class=\"bbp-topic-revision-log-item\">\n		This topic was modified 1 week ago by <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/support/users/kram09890/\" title=\"View kram09890&#039;s profile\" class=\"bbp-author-link\"><span  class=\"bbp-author-name\">kram09890</span></a>.\n	</li>\n\n</ul>\n\n						\n					\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"kram09890\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:67:\"\n					\n					\n					\n					\n					\n\n					\n					\n\n					\n					\n					\n				\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:2:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:103:\"https://wordpress.org/support/topic/xml-sitemap-generator-for-google-for-google-news-and-compatibility/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:187:\"&lt;span class=&quot;resolved&quot; ari